Coderbits,is,a,social,and,professional,network,for,software,developers,and,designers,that,builds,knowledge,portfolios,by,automatically,pulling,profile,data,from,sources,including,GitHub,Stack,Overflow,Dribbble,and,Code,School,Portfolios,are,built,using,source,code,packages,designs,education,organizations,and,more,Coderbits,features,an,award,system,of,badges,and,core,trait,scores,designed,to,be,fun,and,encourage,personal,growth,The,Coderbits,Profile,API,exposes,profile,metadata,by,providing,a,simple,JSON,endpoint,for,every,profile,The,API,also,supports,requests,using,handles,from,linked,external,accounts,The,API,accepts,HTTP,GET,calls,and,supports,JSONP,callbacks